[div class=p 
	"Postman Pat is your typical DS TV show video game released in 2008 and is unsurprisingly comprised of a series of Postman Pat-ified unoriginal minigames. This TAS aims to complete the story mode of this game by playing through all 10 minigames as fast as possible, even if the majority of the run is just waiting for the timer to run out
	$LF
]div
